messages.msgSnippet: If someone told you that there is gold buried in your backyard, would you believe them? Of course not, but I am sure glad I decided to check it out! As a SAHM
messages.messageBody:
If someone told you that there is gold buried in your backyard, would
you believe them? Of course not, but I am sure glad I decided to
check it out! As a SAHM of 5 making ends meet is the eternal
struggle! I have tried a multitude of different savings programs all
of which amounted to a waste of my time. During a gymboree class, I
was discussing the high cost of everything with another couple who
have 7 children. They told me about this program at:
http://www.wrldofproducts.com that allows you to choose the coupons
you want for the products that you already use. My husband and I
thought it was very interesting and decided to try it. About 4 days
after signing on to the program I received my kit in the mail. On
1/25/03, we went shopping at our local Publix Supermarket. I bought
all the items that I normally buy the difference this time was that I
had a coupon for every item that I purchased. The cashier rang up our
order and it came to $327.87 then I presented her with the coupons
that I received through this program and I saved $ 303.79! All I had
to pay was $24.08! The cashier was so shocked that she said, I
thought we were going to have to pay you. I was practically
speechless. This program is the best thing I have ever witnessed.

PS: The company also has 68,000 items at below wholesale prices. It's
amazing!!!
